messages.message: I found an issue with the way some of our python dependencies are getting resolved in the docker container, and I submitted a PR with a proposed solution. While the PR is specifically `image-tasks`, after review and discussion I can start applying it to other builds if we want. https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/10717 is the pull request, https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CD6DST2R0/p1564786257077900 is the thread with more details around the problem.
